{{Quote|I just saw a star disappear.''"<br />"''Sure you did. If the Alliance can make whole stars disappear, we need to surrender now.''"<br />"''No, really. In the Jeweled Lizard. Second star from the end of the tail.|[[Danen]] and [[Caregg Oldathan]]|<ref name="Fury">''[[Legacy of the Force: Fury]]''</ref>}}
The '''Jeweled Lizard''' was a [[Constellation/Legends|constellation]] visible from [[Commenor/Legends|Commenor]]. It was shaped as a lizard, complete with a tail that comprised five [[Star/Legends|stars]]. A [[Cloaking device/Legends|cloaked]] [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] used by the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] during the [[Battle of Commenor (Second Galactic Civil War)|Battle of Commenor]] was detected when one of the stars in the Jeweled Lizard was blocked from the view of a patrolling [[BTL-S8 K-wing assault starfighter]].

